summary: TL*THE CONTACT OWNS A 2008 BIG DOG PITBULL MOTORCYCLE. WHILE DRIVING APPROXIMATELY 65 MPH THE MOTORCYCLE WOULD NOT INCREASE SPEED. THE MOTORCYCLE WAS TAKEN TO THE DEALER WHERE THE TECHNICIANS STATED THAT THE CLUTCH, BEARINGS AND OTHER COMPONENTS WERE  REPLACED. THE MOTORCYCLE WAS IN THE DEALERS POSSESSION FOR ADDITIONAL REPAIRS. THE APPROXIMATE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 7000.
